{"tid":999588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佳士得性醜聞】46歲已婚地產經紀 稱力抗29歲女上司色誘被炒","createTime":"2019-01-28T22:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T02:22:09.000Z","uid":54337,"like":85,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0ae0b41833b85e42e5ac99305d44ca8d88d8a8d1","tid":999588,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T22:18:26.000Z","msg":"【佳士得性醜聞】46歲已婚地產經紀 稱力抗29歲女上司色誘被炒<br />\n<br />\n美國佳士得國際地產公司（Christie's International Real Estate）爆出男下屬疑被年輕17年的女上司性騷擾的醜聞，涉事男下屬稱因「不想背叛太太」而拒絕上司要求，結果被辭退。他控告上司性騷擾及涉各項歧視，又指控公司高層沒處理事件。<br />\n<br />\n涉事46歲男經紀魯米勒（Regis Roumila），控告29歲女上司阿塔米安（Sarine Atamian）歧視及性騷擾，指她利用業務營運經理的職位權力施壓，要求他發展婚外情，包括持續邀請他外出吃晚餐及喝酒，不必要地靠得很近，找藉口觸摸他及整天凝望他。"},{"pid":"e17735fffc387713f436da50edc9c158de9f8eeb","tid":999588,"uid":54337,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T22:18:52.000Z","msg":"案情又指阿塔米安不時品評魯米勒的打扮，包括以「不必要」的語句讚美他的外表、髮型及衣着；企圖擁抱及親吻他，即使魯米勒已表明自己已婚，並且對其他女性沒有興趣，不想背叛太太，阿塔米安仍開口建議他「除了太太以外應該有多一個女友」。<br />\n<br />\n魯米勒在去年8月入職，他聲稱「由首天起」已一直忍受阿塔米安那些苛索，最後於12月10日被辭退，原因是他的「社交模式」與「佳士得文化」不相符。<br />\n<br />\n案件在曼哈頓最高法院審理，魯米勒指阿塔米安涉歧視他的性別、婚姻狀況、家庭崗位、性別取向等。魯米勒同時指控行政總裁庫莫（Kathy Coumou）沒有處理他的投訴，又指佳士得沒有反性騷擾政策，令他因為拒絕「婚外性行為」而被懲罰。阿塔米亞稱上述指控毫無根據。<br />\n<br />\n魯米勒稱他在職時放出價值4900萬美元（約3.8億港元）的樓盤及收盤銷售中賺得超過280萬美元（約2200萬港元），公司尚欠他4.6萬美元（36萬港元）的佣金。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，魯米勒在入職前曾在地產及證券公司「Nest Seekers」工作過5年，於2015年曾成為該公司排名第二位的經紀，在翌年跳槽。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"7a21ceb09c120d8c6bcbc7cb6ce817d2408b8125","tid":999588,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T22:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190129/59193475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59193475&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OAGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=a8cfba83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59193475&h=946da506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190129/59193475</a>"},{"pid":"85dcb839eea77919270132c20bf0dc40ff5ab577","tid":999588,"uid":1713,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T22:19:09.000Z","msg":"女權撚又點睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc6522e8242d86ef678aeb299a7cbe1dcc0516e","tid":999588,"uid":54337,"like":201,"dislike":0,"score":201,"quote":{"pid":"85dcb839eea77919270132c20bf0dc40ff5ab577","tid":999588,"uid":1713,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T22:19:09.000Z","msg":"女權撚又點睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T22:19:44.000Z","msg":"睇唔到囉，仲使問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e79f3a882395f8af7fd9f4e4d24cc57ea77eb3","tid":999588,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T22:22:04.000Z","msg":"26歲？"},{"pid":"68a32d9312f62984a7f3255f9e40760da417a087","tid":999588,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T22:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmetoo"},{"pid":"ea44a4788528c402c1db8256887eac2c38e28043","tid":999588,"uid":20867,"like":165,"dislike":0,"score":165,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T22:53:14.000Z","msg":"肥婆 = 原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527e1324d51a01510716465b2c38c65e9d26971f","tid":999588,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85dcb839eea77919270132c20bf0dc40ff5ab577","tid":999588,"uid":1713,"like":73,"dislike"